data.description: Seller is also MOTIVATED!!! All reasonable offers will be considered!!   Great location and nicely upgraded 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with large 2 car garage is move-in ready. This is a BARGAIN at asking price but Seller is also MOTIVATED!!! The beautiful 32" x 32" PORCELAIN flooring catches your eye immediately and it covers the entire living area throughout the home! The large DREAM KITCHEN features stainless appliances, granite countertops and lots of very pretty cabinets. Checkout the large barn style interior doors that seperate the living room from the family room. The family room has an amazing, huge, wood burnining stone fireplace! All of the bedrooms are very tastefully done ... The AC unit was replaced in 2018. Water heater replaced in 2019. Washer and Dryer are approx. 4 yrs old Roof is approx 10-12 yrs old (per owner). The septic tank located in the front yard was replaced in 2019. The large fenced in backyard would be great for a dog to run around or you could have a garden or just plant several fruit trees and still have plenty of room to add a pool. Fantastic location in the boat ramp community of Gulf Cove! (Membership to the homeowner's association is optional.) The fee for the annual boat ramp decal is currently $65.00 per year. This small fee is a bargain because it gives you both a simple ramp to enter the Myakka River and a beautiful picnic area with ourstanding river views! From your front door you're approx. 15-20 minutes from Englewood Beach or to the Boca Grande bridge! Lots of nice restaurants, tiki bars, and grocery shopping within 5-15 minute drive. If you're a golfer, Riverwood (Par 72 4.5 star golfcourse) is 5 minutes away!!
